Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and the Whitebeards have invaded \Nthe plaza to make it to the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of the Navy's onslaught, \Nwith the Whitebeards' assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally freed Ace! However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for the Answer! Fire Fist \NAce Dies on the Battlefield!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been beaten! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Akainu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Do something about these handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying but... Damn, I can't break them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! He can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He?\N--Yeah, the guy who uncuffed Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the key! Uncuff him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right! Bring him here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this war going to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made you pay for what you've done to \NAce! Have you learned a lesson, Akainu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Is he a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist" Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you let your \Nguard down, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't touch him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just delaying the inevitable, \NJimbei! Since you were once a Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you know what I'm capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to risk my \Nlife if I can delay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been ready to die from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, thank you for helping \Nme! I almost got killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap and uncuff me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V-Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Are \Nyou losing your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better keep holding me \Ndown like that, Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you don't, I will kill Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I need to execute a traitor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys are Haki users!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we let that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have more regret about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that it's too \Nlate to save "Fire Fist?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, you need to get treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you pushed yourself that far but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't make it all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please help Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey somebody! Help Ace! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry! This way! Give him first aid now!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let me see the wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Hurry up and help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Just do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you a doctor?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My organs have been burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold out any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that my life is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inject that stuff into Ace! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you did to me, why can't you help Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I beg you! Please! Help! Help Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please inject that into Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace boy... can't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you'd never die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold out any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you'd never die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I even deserve to have been born?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Gold Roger had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know what'd happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd get his head cut off for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm not content if \Nwe kill him that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we prick him with a needle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once for every grudge that \Nsomeone holds against Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Instead, we'll burn him alive first
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and humiliate him prior to death \Nin front of the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody will say "that serves him right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear from him as he dies:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry I was born! I'm \Njust a piece of trash!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that he ever had a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wanted me to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! You caused trouble in the city again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making a fuss about \Nit! Don't give us a hard time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening, Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up, Dadan!\N--What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were stronger, I would \Nhave killed all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even have a will to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it weren't for Sabo and a \Nhigh-maintenance brother like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. If you see Dadan \Nsomeday, say hello for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I face my own death, I \Neven miss a woman like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't say that you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing that makes me wanna stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my desire to see \Nyou fulfill your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure that you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live as we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we promised that \Nday, I have no regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! Don't tell a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something tells me that what \NI truly wanted was not fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I deserve to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted was the \Nanswer for that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell me that my \Nbeloved son is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna save you even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Rescue Ace and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...destroy the Navy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get Ace back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't raise my voice to let \Neverybody hear me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what I'm about to say now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for loving someone like \Nme who is good for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and who has such bad blood in his veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...up to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I deserved to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll see as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a reality difficult to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's death cruelly unfolds \Nbefore Luffy's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle does not pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the pursuit intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard's rage shakes all of Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Navy Headquarters Falls! \NWhitebeard's Unspeakable Wrath!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
